## Compilation:

Under the cs488 directory do the following:

    $ cd A2
    $ premake4 gmake
    $ make

To run the program, type the command:

    $ ./A2

This program is tested on the VM and lab computer gl33.

---

##Manual:

---

Initial scale is 0.25
Initial lookForm point is (0, 0, 3)
lookAt point is (0,0,1)
Up point is (0,1,0)
Initial near plane has z value 1
Initial far plane has z value 5
The Translation of view and model and Scale of model factor is 0.0005
The Rotation of view and model factor is 0.01
Change in Field of View factor is 0.1
Change in far and near plane z value has a factor of 0.005